complex number poruthavara, oru complex number ku 2nd root find panna 2 different values kadaikum and 3rd root find panninga na 3 different values kadaikum.

so ipo naa 3rd find panna 3 values varum la.

idhula first value value find panna k ku 0 nu substitute panni value find pannanum.
next 2nd value find panna 1 substitue pannanum and
3rd value find panna k ku 2 nu substitute pannanum.

